name: Vader's Cybernetic Enhancements
Lore: 'Users of the Force can mysteriously manipulate their own physiology and psychology. Control allows rapid healing and provides some immunity to pain, poison and disease.',
Text: 'Deploy on [Vader] Vader.  Vader may move as a ''react.''  Your battle destiny draws here are +1.  Opponent''s cards deployed on Vader are canceled.  If Vader about to be placed in Lost Pile, may lose 4 Force to take him (and a lightsaber he was armed with, if possible) into hand. (Immune to Alter.)',
